        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"598183\">@Oliver Bertuch</span> introduced us to <a href=\"https://github.com/diffplug/spotless\">Spotless</a> for formatting code in <a href=\"https://github.com/gdcc/xoai\">https://github.com/gdcc/xoai</a></p>\n<p>From the README:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\"><pre><span></span><code>mvn spotless:apply\n# - or to just check for consistency use -\nmvn spotless:check\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>It works great! Should we use it with the main code base?</p>",
        "id": 432974039,
        "sender_full_name": "Philip Durbin ðŸš€",
        "timestamp": 1712952358
    },
    {
